          <physDesc>
            <objectDesc>
              <supportDesc material="parchment">
                <support>
                  <p>Fol. <ref target="https://corpuscoranicum.de/en/verse-navigator/sura/6/verse/71/manuscripts/1785/page/1r">1 recto</ref> is flesh side, fol. <ref target="https://corpuscoranicum.de/en/verse-navigator/sura/6/verse/71/manuscripts/1785/page/1v">1 verso</ref> is hair side. </p>
                  <p>Text division: Simple verse separators consist of a cluster of three strokes arranged one above  the other in the shape of an arrow. Verse separators after ten verses are illuminated with gold, red and brown ink. </p>
                </support>
                <extent>Folios: 1
                                    <dimensions unit="mm"><width>255</width><height>192</height></dimensions>
                                </extent>
